                <p
                    class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed"
                    style="font-family: var(--font-body); line-height: 1.7;"
                >
                    Award-winning bartenders who transform cocktail making into
                    an art form, each drink a masterpiece
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
